OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fto end the day and remaining dry
OL,7,Fovernight with clear periods
OL,8,Fdeveloping. The wind eases in most
OL,9,Fplaces though remaining breezy along
OL,10,Fthe coast. Temperatures relatively
OL,11,Fmild overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FBreezy at times with variable
OL,14,Fcloud for much of the period, staying
OL,15,Fmostly dry. Temperatures likely above
OL,16,Faverage, becoming very warm or hot in
OL,17,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
