OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSome
OL,6,Fcloudy periods on Monday and Tuesday,
OL,7,Fturning sunnier by Wednesday and
OL,8,Fremaining mostly dry throughout.
OL,9,FBecoming very warm or hot in places as
OL,10,Ftemperatures increase.
